<item>
            <title>Version 1.0.9</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>⚡️EQ 1.0.9</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Rebuilt settings engine — controls no longer reset at playback stop/start; panel, inspector, and saved projects stay in sync</li>
                    <li>Fixes the settings churn during playback reported on 1.0.8</li>
                    <li>New reset controls: Reset All (also resets the inspector), Reset Shape, Reset Sliders</li>
                    <li>Microphone choice holds reliably; re-picking the same mic no longer changes other settings</li>
                    <li>"Remove Voice Reverb" is now "De-Reverb"</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 17:40:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/ludwig-ship-it/powereq_updates/releases/download/v1.0.9/PowerEQ-1.0.9.pkg"
