<item>
            <title>Version 1.0.8</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>⚡️EQ 1.0.8</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Redesigned control panel — tabbed layout, larger controls, nothing scrolls</li>
                    <li>New Microphone selection in the panel and Final Cut's inspector; saves with the project</li>
                    <li>Copying the effect to another clip now carries all settings and Analyze results</li>
                    <li>Settings survive closing and reopening projects far more reliably</li>
                    <li>Analyze responds immediately; Advanced sliders and inspector stay in sync</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
