<item>
            <title>Version 1.0.7</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>⚡️EQ 1.0.7</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Advanced sliders (Clarity, Brightness, Reduce Boom, and friends) no longer reset to default when Final Cut starts playback</li>
                    <li>Analyze results hold on more reliably — room-control settings are no longer reverted by Final Cut on play</li>
                    <li>Reset now clears all processing, including hidden room-control settings</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
