<item>
            <title>Version 1.0.6</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>⚡️EQ 1.0.6</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixes automatic updates: the app previously reported the wrong internal version, causing repeated "update available" prompts after updating</li>
                    <li>Fixes a rare crash when reopening a Final Cut Pro project during playback</li>
                    <li>Analyze results saved with a project are no longer overwritten when the project is reopened</li>
                    <li>The Analyze button no longer spins forever if playback isn't running — it now offers a hint instead</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
